    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nWhen ui2 is enabled, indenting with `=` pops up two messages, opening up the message window:\n\n<img width=\"865\" height=\"561\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/25b09168-d1e1-49b5-b733-5e1dce5e7262\" />\n\nWith ui1 this is only displayed as a single line:\n\n<img width=\"865\" height=\"561\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/52aa7a2e-1fd4-49f0-8fa5-2610255df294\" />\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nUse `|progress-message|`s for the built-in indentation (or don't display anything; it can be a bit noisy and is typically instant).",
